=== Transitive verb ===
'''efface''' ('''effeced''', '''effacing''')
# To cause to [[disappear]] (as anything impressed or inscribed upon a surface) by rubbing out or striking out
#to erase; to render illegible or [[indiscernible]]; as, to efface the letters on a [[monument]], or the inscription on a coin.

